Summary: Saw an intense green light falling from the sky seemed to slow down
divs: Sighting DetailsMy son and I were walking home from the store last night when we got about two blocks away from home, I don't know why but happened to look up,and I saw a very intense almost florecent light rapidly fallig from the sky, I grabbed my son Josh and screamed "did you just see that!" and he said he didn't see anything.He asked what I saw and I told him I saw a very intense green colored light almost florecent falling from the sky. I knew it wasn't anything I'd seen before and while it was visible and falling it almost seemed to slow down. I really don't know what it was, but I told my son I've just witnessed either a UFO or a meteor, alls I know was I was left with a definite unsettled feeling, He gave me a funny look so I shrugged it off and we finished the walk home. I know I watched it till it went behind the apartment building in front of us, thats it thats all there is. But I hope I wasn't the only one to see it!
